           SHORT="RealtimeKit is a D-Bus system service"

cat << EOF
ealtimeKit is a D-Bus system service that changes the scheduling policy of user processes/threads to SCHED_RR
(i.e. realtime scheduling mode) on request. It is intended to be used as a secure mechanism to allow real-time
scheduling to be used by normal user processes.
EOF
